de.awi.floenavigation.synchronization

Class Users

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.awi.floenavigation.synchronization.Users

  • public class Users
extends java.lang.Object
    Creates an Admin User object with getters and setters for all the parameters of a DatabaseHelper.usersTable Table in Database. Used by UsersSync to create a new User Object to be inserted in to the Database.
    See Also:
    SyncActivity, UsersSync, de.awi.floenavigation.synchronization
